===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:44:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:44:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:39')

time:::0.00042510032653809

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:39') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00053501129150391

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00047993659973145

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:40') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:40')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00034379959106445

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:41') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:41')

time:::0.00044608116149902

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 09:49:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00042510032653809

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:38') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:38') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:38')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00062680244445801

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:38') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:41') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:41')

time:::0.00024986267089844

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00024890899658203

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:42') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:42') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:42')

time:::0.00023388862609863

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:42') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:43') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00046610832214355

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:43') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:43') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:43')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00033903121948242

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:43') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44')

time:::0.00046896934509277

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44')

time:::0.00023484230041504

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00025606155395508

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:44') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57')

time:::0.00049209594726562

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57')

time:::0.00022506713867188

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:58') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:58') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00039911270141602

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00037503242492676

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:58') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id

                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.00031304359436035

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59')

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:04:59') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00045108795166016

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:05:00') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:38') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:38')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.0004570484161377

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:38') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.0004279613494873

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:39') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00029802322387695

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:40') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.00052285194396973

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:53') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00027704238891602

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:53') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:54') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:54')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00024199485778809

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

time:::0.00049114227294922

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:55') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:55')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00037503242492676

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00024318695068359

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:56') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:56')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00033998489379883

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:57') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00075006484985352

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:57')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00024008750915527

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00031089782714844

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:58') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:58')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00028514862060547

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:31:58') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))

time:::0.00045895576477051

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00045204162597656

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00049710273742676

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

time:::0.00027608871459961

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:17') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:17') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:17') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:17') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:18')

time:::0.00044989585876465

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:18') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:18') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:19') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:19')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.0003359317779541

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 10:32:19') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00052189826965332

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15')

time:::0.00045609474182129

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:16')

time:::0.0005497932434082

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:07:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:23') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:23') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00048708915710449

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.0030758380889893

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:23') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.00032711029052734

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:23') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:24')

time:::0.00045895576477051

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:24') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:24') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:24') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:25')

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:25') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:25') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:25') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:26')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00035285949707031

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:26') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:26') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00032806396484375

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:39') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:40') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00033688545227051

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:42') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:42')

time:::0.00023794174194336

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:42') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
