				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:42')

time:::0.00024294853210449

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:42') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:54') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:54') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00046992301940918

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00045299530029297

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

time:::0.00024294853210449

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.0003659725189209

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00042891502380371

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00056982040405273

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:57')

time:::0.00026202201843262

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:09:57') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:15') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:15') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00035190582275391

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:15') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00027608871459961

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00027203559875488

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:16') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:17') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:18') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.0016269683837891

===========

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:18') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00057697296142578

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00058698654174805

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:18') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:18')

time:::0.00046896934509277

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:18') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:53') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00042295455932617

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00045895576477051

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:53') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00053811073303223

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:53') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:54')

time:::0.00026106834411621

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55')

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00082612037658691

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:55') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00023508071899414

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00046586990356445

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:10:56') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:09') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:10') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:10') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

time:::0.00031709671020508

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:10') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00032305717468262

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:10') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:11') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:11') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:11') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.0008389949798584

time:::0.00073003768920898

===========

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC
		

time:::0.00028705596923828

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00025796890258789

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00033092498779297

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:12') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail

				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

time:::0.00033187866210938

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:11:46') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:13:36') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:13:36') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:14:41') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:14:41') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

time:::0.00034618377685547

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:14:41') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54')

time:::0.0003352165222168

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54')

time:::0.00037598609924316

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:15:54') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:16:04') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:16:10') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:16:10')

time:::0.00049090385437012

===========

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:16:10') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC

				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16,22,30,36,42,5,11) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:20:48') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT id, promotion_id, product_id, quantity, quantity_user, sold, price, percent, `type`, date_end, date_start 
				FROM fs_promotion_discount_detail 
				WHERE published = 1 AND product_id IN (1,7,13,19,27,33,39,2,8,14,20,28,34,40,3,9,15,21,29,35,41,4,10,16) AND DATE(date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:20:48') 
				AND ((quantity > 0 AND sold < quantity) OR (quantity = 0)) ORDER BY date_start DESC

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

SELECT a.id, a.name, a.alias, a.image, a.quantity, a.price, b.product_id, b.promotion_id, b.quantity AS discount_quantity, b.quantity_user, b.sold AS discount_sold, b.price AS discount_price, b.percent, b.`type`, b.date_end, b.date_start 
                FROM fs_products AS a INNER JOIN fs_promotion_discount_detail AS b ON a.id = b.product_id 
                WHERE b.published = 1 AND a.published = 1 AND a.price > 0 AND DATE(b.date_end) >= DATE('2024-03-31 21:20:48') AND ((b.quantity > 0 AND b.sold < b.quantity) OR (b.quantity = 0))
                ORDER BY a.ordering DESC, a.id DESC 
        

time:::0.0010421276092529

				FROM fs_banners AS a
				WHERE published = 1  AND category_id IN (1)   
				ORDER BY ordering, id

				FROM fs_menus_items
